title: Spacious Studio 1 Bath in the Financial District!
posting_body: ['Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'Spacious Studio 1 Bath that features stainless steel appliances, hardwood floors, natural light, and marble bathrooms!', 'This luxury building provides a 24-hour doorman, fitness center, resident lounge with wifi and billiards, roof deck with views of East River and gas grills.', 'Located in the heart of the Financial District which features an all-access transportation hub including major subway lines (A/C/J/Z/2/3/4/5/R/W), PATH, and NYC ferries.', 'This neighborhood features local restaurants, attractions, and beautiful waterfront views to enjoy the city!', 'LISTING #138525', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Subway', 'Laundry', 'Lounge', 'Roof Deck', 'Wheelchair Access', 'Common Outdoor Space', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood', 'Marble Bath', 'Light', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Sabrina Rosal', 'Phone: 201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>', 'To view, call or text Sabrina Rosal at:', '201-350-7865', 'Email: <URL>']
